hopobject.name: Page
hopobject.body: Whereabouts are you from? clean energy patch Brooklyn Decker, Sports Illustrated cover model and wife of tennis star Andy Roddick, has a message for men: keep your ego in check and play things straight. In the February 2011 issue of Esquire, the blond bombshell opens up about Nicole Kidman's acting advice, the one chicken dish she can make well (it involves prosciutto) and how men need to be more honest with women. Her advice to men: 'Men need to learn to put everything on the table,' Decker told Esquire. 'Just put everything on the table. And when it comes to the game playing, enough.'
